  <description>
    <p>Mindwtr is a local-first task manager built around Getting Things Done. It helps you capture tasks quickly, organize projects and areas, and review your work without locking your data into a cloud service.</p>
    <p>The desktop app includes recurring tasks, calendar views, attachments, local sync folders, and optional Dropbox, WebDAV, or self-hosted cloud sync. Your data stays readable on disk and works offline by default.</p>
  </description>
